lu.uni.geko.common
Class GeKoBridge

java.lang.Object
  lu.uni.geko.common.GeKoBridge

public final class GeKoBridge
extends Object

A utility class containing methods that are used by multiple GeKo plug-ins and that are GeKo specific (so they do not belong to an adapter class of lu.uni.geko.util.bridges).

(Note that it is disputable whether this class conforms to the bridge pattern as we are currently only providing one implementation and the "abstractions" can be regarded as low-level.)

getRegisteredExtensionsInDescPriority

public static <T> List<T> getRegisteredExtensionsInDescPriority(String extensionPointID,
                                                                Class<T> extensionClass)
Returns a list that contains all registered extensions for the default GeKo class property of the given extension point ID if the property is an instance of the given class for all registered extensions and if the default GeKo priority property exists. The list is ordered by decreasing priority (i.e. starting with the extension having the highest integer value priority).

Type Parameters:
T - the type of the extension point property
Parameters:
extensionPointID - the ID of the extension point to be inspected
extensionClass - the class of the extension point property
Returns:
a list containing the registered extensions ordered by decreasing priority

getRegisteredExtensionsWithPriority

public static <T> List<Pair<T,Integer>> getRegisteredExtensionsWithPriority(String extensionPointID,
                                                                            Class<T> extensionClass)
Returns a list that contains all registered extensions for the default GeKo class property of the given extension point ID together with their priority property if the property is an instance of the given class for all registered extensions and if the default GeKo priority property exists. The list is not sorted in any particular order.

Type Parameters:
T - the type of the extension point property
Parameters:
extensionPointID - the ID of the extension point to be inspected
extensionClass - the class of the extension point property
Returns:
a list containing the registered extensions together with their priority
